prevalence:流行率,患病率
true positive rate/sensitivity:患者测试呈阳性概率
true negative rate/specificity:未患病者测试呈阴性概率

Test goal: gain knowledge of unobserved parameter from observed data.
Sampling/data distribution: conditional distribution of data y given parameter theta-data distribution under different scenerios for theta.
Prior distribution: marginal distribution of theta-our state of knowledge prior to observing y.
Posterior distribution: conditional distribution of theta given y-our state of knowledge after observing y.

Random Variable: a quantity whose uncertainty can be measured in terms of probability.

Conditional independence - independence 不充分不必要
